{
  "stem": "39.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, we leaved everything in the house, so they took everything what was in the house later on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We brought our own food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it was not too much food, but it was sort of enough.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People got along very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As we were standing in line in front of the bathroom, but nobody made a big deal out of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, all the mothers in that one kitchen to cook, it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, actually, we didn't make a deal of all those things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only thing it mattered at that time, just the families to remain together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We thought that we shall be in the ghetto for a long time, but no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ghetto was a very temporary solution, situation at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Like in our city, we were 18,000 Jews in the ghetto from our city, from the surrounding smaller cities, and from the surrounding villages.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as the time was passing, it was already approximately May the 14 or 15 when the newest regulation, it was that we are going to be taken away, relocated, as you said, in a working camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were told that the families are going to be together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were three groups taken come from the ghetto, each time 6,000 people, to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This I thought started approximately, as I told you, May the 14, something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So these were the deportations, the rounding up for the deportations?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were not told where is the working camp, somewhere in a working camp, that's all, no name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the last group taken from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was May 31st, 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
